{"tid":1038621,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(叫春)原來要放低真係一件幾難嘅事","createTime":"2019-02-26T20:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T01:40:04.000Z","uid":58080,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef697b14651a28ec681450b490704a88d8aa00e","tid":1038621,"uid":58080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:07:34.000Z","msg":"同個女仔識咗2個幾月 單獨出過幾次街<br />\n<br />\n同佢性格幾夾幾啱傾 同佢相處亦好開心 <br />\n<br />\n甚至前個排兩個人去咗AIA嘉年華玩<br />\n<br />\n但佢有晚突然同我講話會同男仔單獨出街 <br />\n<br />\n仲講笑咁講話 ：話唔定我今晚就出pool呢<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢係想我呷醋想我表態<br />\n<br />\n原本想約佢今個星期話有嘢想當面講<br />\n<br />\n最後因為一句有咩唔可以依家講拒絕咗<br />\n<br />\n而呢句亦都係我地對話既最後一句<br />\n<br />\n原來一切都係自己諗多咗<br />\n<br />\n尋晚已經斷咗聯絡 但係個心好唔舒服 求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7847db4ca9bbb50a63ebc68e320e09bdd4faaff7","tid":1038621,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:08:31.000Z","msg":"上網識？"},{"pid":"85999878d31f98c3f44479cf9fe0451c20257d92","tid":1038621,"uid":58080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7847db4ca9bbb50a63ebc68e320e09bdd4faaff7","tid":1038621,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:08:31.000Z","msg":"上網識？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:09:10.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39112ffe1a9d969c5a0068205cf906b56fbf269c","tid":1038621,"uid":127033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:10:24.000Z","msg":"難都唔洗開3個pi既"},{"pid":"47b768d6124ca74b6705ec953a757cc0524db5a3","tid":1038621,"uid":58080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39112ffe1a9d969c5a0068205cf906b56fbf269c","tid":1038621,"uid":127033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:10:24.000Z","msg":"難都唔洗開3個pi既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"手機出po bug咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3205847255b71